Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:55.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接連著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:01:08.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口難開 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:14.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}漸次斑駁  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:21.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至終焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:27.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之間  逢見君影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:31.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:43.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故鄉迢迢  時之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:49.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無愛無心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:02:01.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻蒼空
